title: Neff Hooks Up With DJ Drama & DJ Infamous
description:
NEFF hooked up with music producer Cory Moe to rent out his MAD Studios in Atlanta to shoot this campaign picking MAD Studios gave us privacy to be creative and think outside the box with enough space for a BBQ lunch that day. DJ Drama was a natural fit for NEFF to work with on this Campaign when you trying to Feed the Streets! 
He remains One of the Hottest DJs in the streets wit 3 Huge releases this year, 2 Chainz TRU tape, 50 cent & Meek Mills Dream chasers 2, which had over 1 million downloads first day! You can't hit Atlanta without having DJ Infamous who is Ludacris Official Tour DJ be apart of the Fall Winter Push. He found time out of his schedule to join us as well. Check out the Video footage behind the scenes of the Shoot
